{
  "description": "A breathtaking panoramic view of a rugged coastline meeting the vast expanse of the ocean. The foreground features a steep, verdant cliff covered in lush greenery, with some vegetation extending into the frame. Turquoise waves crash against the rocky shore, creating a frothy white edge where they meet the land. The ocean transitions from a vibrant turquoise near the shore to a deep navy blue further out. In the distance, the coastline continues, shrouded in a soft, ethereal mist that blends with the horizon, creating a sense of depth and mystery. The sky is a clear, bright blue, providing a beautiful contrast to the sea and land. The overall composition conveys a sense of natural beauty, tranquility, and the raw power of the ocean.",
